text: Jan Holmlund (born 29 March 1957) is a Swedish ski jumper. He competed in the normal hill and large hill events at the 1980 Winter Olympics. ==References== Category:1957 births Category:Living people Category:Swedish male ski jumpers Category:Olympic ski jumpers of Sweden Category:Ski jumpers at the 1980 Winter Olympics Category:People from Norrbotten County
